'''[[Negishi]] [[coupling]]'''

#{{chemistry}} a class of [[reaction]]s in which an [[organic]] [[halide]] reacts with an [[organometallic]] [[zinc]] compound under the control of a [[catalyst]]; R-X + R'-Zn-X' => R-R'

